1S pass 2S pass 3C pass 3S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[Category "Basic Bidding"]
[Difficulty "beginner"]
[SkillPath "basic_bidding/major_suit_openings"]
[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.  

With 7 points and good trumps you respond 2\S. Partner now bids 3\C.  

Again partner is inviting you to bid game. He wants you to bid it if you are at the top of your 6-10 range, and he wants you to particularly promote any Help you can give him in \Cs.

You are at the bottom of your range and you have no help in \Cs, so you just return to \Ss. Partner passes.}

